## Architecture technique

```
InputForm (UI)
    ↓
POST /api/project-context/analyze
    ↓
fetchRepoMetadata()
    ↓ (GitHub API v3)
    ├── getRepoInfo()
    ├── getTree() (recursive)
    └── getPackageJson()
    ↓
analyzeProject()
    ↓
    ├── detectFramework()
    ├── detectLanguage()
    ├── detectArchitecture()
    ├── detectORM()
    ├── detectDatabase()
    ├── detectStateManagement()
    ├── detectBuildTool()
    └── detectTestFramework()
    ↓
generateNotes() (template-based)
    ↓
ProjectContext
    ↓
Response avec cache
```

